    </section>

    <!-- Summary Section -->
    <section class="mt-12 py-8 bg-om-gold/10 rounded-xl shadow-md border-l-4 border-om-gold">
      <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-om-navy px-6 mb-3">Compass and Dashboard</h4>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed px-6">
        By implementing this comprehensive performance management approach, OMSB ensures **transparency and accountability** throughout the transformation. The leadership will have visibility at all times into what’s working and what’s not, enabling proactive management. Moreover, by aligning with national KPIs and continuously measuring progress, OMSB positions itself to achieve high scores in formal digital government evaluations – but more importantly, to truly realize the promised improvements in service delivery and institutional capacity. As this is a long-term transformation, these monitoring mechanisms serve as the **compass and dashboard** that keep OMSB guided toward its 2036 targets, ensuring the journey yields real benefits at every stage.
      </p>
